1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T18:12:03.000Z","msg":"搭單討論<br />\n有冇人斷後十字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n照mri睇到斷左一半未斷哂，醫生唔建議做手術<br />\n斷左就黎4個月，醫生話要一年先可以做正常運動<br />\n斷左到而家都冇跳過冇跑過，落樓梯曲嗰下唔太食到力<br />\n有冇人有經驗斷唔哂既話條韌帶會唔會增生/增厚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4cdc30d897dd7e01ed4db322fd98fac6e710df3","tid":1132951,"uid":103269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec77d6426a0825ad69fa71ec50a7870889e90c9d","tid":1132951,"uid":135961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b2feb5aa4f87c25361cb7cfa4c4d17606201267","tid":1132951,"uid":103269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad639097e6999ca4ea5d741f57ccf261d2013107","tid":1132951,"uid":135961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T18:00:15.000Z","msg":"用左個條整<br />\n直情係痛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T18:06:56.000Z","msg":"3個星期前做完手術，宜家先屈到90度多啲啲，日日都用健身球輔助去屈但個位又緊又痛扯到實一實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   會唔會太慢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T18:09:51.000Z","msg":"好似會關你傷咩位事<br />\n<br />\n我只係整十字冇傷半月板<br />\n而家都屈到90度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T19:06:04.000Z","msg":"我都係靜係整十字，不過見物理治療師話我呢個range太慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a5ebbd6260cc4aff77b67774c15fc27429dc68e","tid":1132951,"uid":224831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T21:08:25.000Z","msg":"好多年前 中三個陣斷前十字+半月板碎裂<br />\n印象中好似做佐成年物理治療<br />\n但頭幾年行動都覺得翻唔到整親之前既感覺<br />\n有時會肋肋聲 平衝又會差佐啲<br />\n<br />\n直到近幾年就好似冇乜野"},{"pid":"a4de515b30c173ae94ec97546e9d20d3f3350ad3","tid":1132951,"uid":71737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T23:22:02.000Z","msg":"手術做完已經5年<br />\n最緊要keep住練腳嘅肌肉<br />\n就唔會有唔穩陣嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecc10297c94dfb449b7ed1bb91f80b497d3e42a0","tid":1132951,"uid":79609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-