:1132951,"uid":2481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T18:15:28.000Z","msg":"我三月頭踢波整斷十字韌帶，好在有買保險，兩日後即刻去海港城睇骨科醫生，一個星期內就喺聖保祿醫院做完手術，用後大腿根，早期後邊大比真係痛到飛起，一個月後已經冇咁痛，而家係私家物理治療師度操緊，行路已經正常返，醫生話要一步一步慢慢段練，話大部份人可以半年內做一般運動，埋單找數要10 萬 ，好在claim得足。"},{"pid":"082ea520601777a97642cd60509772e5c8b8d621","tid":1132951,"uid":60481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e8267b0f7ff00c2be72c15a744cf6dab122880c","tid":1132951,"uid":2481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T18:15:28.000Z","msg":"我三月頭踢波整斷十字韌帶，好在有買保險，兩日後即刻去海港城睇骨科醫生，一個星期內就喺聖保祿醫院做完手術，用後大腿根，早期後邊大比真係痛到飛起，一個月後已經冇咁痛，而家係私家物理治療師度操緊，行路已經正常返，醫生話要一步一步慢慢段練，話大部份人可以半年內做一般運動，埋單找數要10 萬 ，好在claim得足。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T19:27:28.000Z","msg":"我都係聖保祿"},{"pid":"5c9548c19b59cb97aec12857096fc8c14822f1be","tid":1132951,"uid":58413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T20:17:57.000Z","msg":"我2005年響聯合做<br />\n波就無再踼<br />\n家下都係跑步同游水。最多跑5k同只能游自由式。<br />\n唔做運動會鬆。"},{"pid":"5fb2c4cb60d0132b1b6850c490197340486790ca","tid":1132951,"uid":57461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5523a8275e246545f0efe021e2a46876429c31f3","tid":1132951,"uid":79609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36d919dffbe4376be3cba816bcf5632579493fe5","tid":1132951,"uid":57461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T00:35:13.000Z","msg":"兩年幾前做左acl同半月板<br />\n前幾日睇mri report又斷左<br />\n同傷埋半月板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實都唔知點傷 一直努力練野 無特別操過份or做危險野 <br />\n而家要簡正整半月板 or 兩樣搞晒 <br />\n而家27歲 鍾意打波做運動 ...<br />\n驚痛 驚又要練返 唉<br />\n有冇師兄俾到意見我？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T17:48:29.000Z","msg":"又斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T23:58:26.000Z","msg":"係呀 都唔係好肯定點斷 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而定仲諗緊做邊樣 唉"},{"pid":"cbfaac06ce29b6ed14fa2373c3d49cc49fd83637","tid":1132951,"uid":159928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T00:27:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5fe184c79f0a9b31f3074ae6eb8b40ded76325f","tid":1132951,"uid":202466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T00:30:18.000Z","msg":"最傷係個心態，兩邊先後斷過，做左手術。就算好返，但個恐懼係擺脫唔到，心理上已經自廢左武功。"},{"pid":"ba1f9cc8554a48650dd1e0d38c1c13c7738362c8","tid":1132951,"uid":165028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T00:33:40.000Z","msg":"我有個朋友玩體操<br />\n有次跳馬做轉體動作早左落地<br />\n前後兩條一次過斷哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbd3d3c4856a68223fc8b698b0e7eac0fb8deefe","tid":1132951,"uid":73302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c0077dfa26bafc7067586c28fc6a32f684ee703","tid":1132951,"uid":120427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52fa57249754123c2a6b3e818bef36459089f831","tid":1132951,"uid":135961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87761da328de1c971cabde83f873076f48f4eb82","tid":1132951,"uid":120427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:55:29.000Z","msg":"15年斷左，做完手術一直做PHYSIO<br />\n三個月可能跑步，八個月打返波，講真俾個PHYISO咁TRAIN法，仲勁過未斷之前<br />\n不過上年又傷多次，冇斷但成好有啲鬆，所以之後都冇打波。我覺得最緊要係勤力，操返好就可以打返波"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T11:17:41.000Z","msg":"你跟邊個physio<br />\n利申岩岩做完手術<br />\n4日就行到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T02:06:59.000Z","msg":"我睇吳俊霆(Elton Ng)操得好甘<br />\n睇Physio有埋Personal Trainer嘅服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過依家出名左booking好爆，要預早book<br />\n利申都係3/4日就行到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T19:41:17.000Z","msg":"巴打有無話幾錢睇一次？<br />\n有無tg留底傾下"},{"pid":"a76e328b9cea5c281a3c04df3bfb43f7e2fd3534","tid":1132951,"uid":32437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T19:45:48.000Z","msg":"三年前斷<br />\n抖左半年<br />\n而家做運動同以前無分別<br />\n不過始終會感覺到同原本有分別"},{"pid":"6ebedbaa6f55fcd6de0b1c03c4558aa8f848eace","tid":1132951,"uid":30154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T19:49:26.000Z","msg":"斷過acl都裂過半月板 <br />\n個人經驗之談，唔好太在意人地做完手術幾耐就跑得打得波，自己進度慢過人。<br />\n就算傷同一樣野，同一個手術，每個人身體反應都唔同，本身運動水平、體質、恢復情況都唔同。<br />\n但大前提一定係要好勤力操<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3657ba453a73c443f976f3790801973332ff5752","tid":1132951,"uid":32437,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c6c1d9162d03c4457d90676b549993e5d20dd99b","tid":1132951,"uid":133555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T18:12:03.000Z","msg":"搭單討論<br />\n有冇人斷後十字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n照mri睇到斷左一半未斷哂，醫生唔建議做手術<br />\n斷左就黎4個月，醫生話要一年先可以做正常運動<br />\n斷左到而家都冇跳過冇跑過，落樓梯曲嗰下唔太食到力<br />\n有冇人有經驗斷唔哂既話條韌帶會唔會增生/增厚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T19:52:41.000Z","msg":"面對現實<br />\n職業球員都係斷左就係得番咁多<br />\n聽人講過外國有d先進嘅方法定期打針會令條韌帶唔做手術都做到運動<br />\n兩三皮一支一年打幾次打到老"},{"pid":"896641a509107b09f13f04b74e5fd95049366492","tid":1132951,"uid":57109,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T20:02:00.000Z","msg":"過來人分享吓 <br />\n身邊運動都好多人斷十字 連埋自己 我諗有10個<br />\n講真我到今時今日某d位落地 打籃球 轉向 or射波大家時都會突然feel到鬆咗一鬆 個膝頭移咗一移 但跟住又無咩事呀<br />\n<br />\n實際你見外國球員球星斷過十字 有專人or隊醫跟出跟入 都未必去番最高峰 你就知要完全recover既重要性<br />\n<br />\n唔好話日日 香港地一星期做三日物理治療要堅持3個月都唔易啦 放完工趕頭趕命去睇physio 當時堅持左一個月就頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"853e8fa0e1eba03a9553e9e22cc5d02d1f822142","tid":1132951,"uid":250415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T03:25:24.000Z","msg":"右腳斷過2次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n16年尾斷17年1月做手術 10月嗰陣再斷過<br />\n磨到今年2月先再做手術"},{"pid":"56594aca8f9072fb7412a89f2713959f37f9b6f0","tid":1132951,"uid":19906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"853e8fa0e1eba03a9553e9e22cc5d02d1f822142","tid":1132951,"uid":250415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T03:25:24.000Z","msg":"右腳斷過2次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n16年尾斷17年1月做手術 10月嗰陣再斷過<br />\n磨到今年2月先再做手術"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T03:33:53.000Z","msg":"做過咩唔夠一年又斷? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf41223a541d8510c98fdd01961f4e651a1862d2","tid":1132951,"uid":250415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T03:46:29.000Z","msg":"走左去踢波<br />\n醫生講明話術後9個月可以掂下個波 但只限輕鬆地踢下<br />\n但我就落場比賽 結果一下跳起落地就GG 了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5abe4c6cae8c0cf34836e5a9fc3a3fd6711529c3","tid":1132951,"uid":250415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56594aca8f9072fb7412a89f2713959f37f9b6f0","tid":1132951,"uid":19906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"853e8fa0e1eba03a9553e9e22cc5d02d1f822142","tid":1132951,"uid":250415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T03:25:24.000Z","msg":"右腳斷過2次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n16年尾斷17年1月做手術 10月嗰陣再斷過<br />\n磨到今年2月先再做手術"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T03:33:53.000Z","msg":"做過咩唔夠一年又斷? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T03:46:52.000Z","msg":"走左去踢波<br />\n醫生講明話術後9個月可以掂下個波 但只限輕鬆地踢下<br />\n但我就落場比賽 結果一下跳起落地就GG 了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ff5c7439ab8623d940aad1b5c62a88b208f86c7","tid":1132951,"uid":19906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5abe4c6cae8c0cf34836e5a9fc3a3fd6711529c3","tid":1132951,"uid":250415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56594aca8f9072fb7412a89f2713959f37f9b6f0","tid":1132951,"uid":19906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"853e8fa0e1eba03a9553e9e22cc5d02d1f822142","tid":1132951,"uid":250415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T03:25:24.000Z","msg":"右腳斷過2次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n16年尾斷17年1月做手術 10月嗰陣再斷過<br />\n磨到今年2月先再做手術"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T03:33:53.000Z","msg":"做過咩唔夠一年又斷? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T03:46:52.000Z","msg":"走左去踢波<br />\n醫生講明話術後9個月可以掂下個波 但只限輕鬆地踢下<br />\n但我就落場比賽 結果一下跳起落地就GG 了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T04:12:46.000Z","msg":"慘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我做完手術7個月, 有hea打下波, 不過有時都驚唔小心又整斷"},{"pid":"2cd309b847e6da01ba3c9df977aa4a6cf8652acc","tid":1132951,"uid":178236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T04:22:37.000Z","msg":"我acl 都有7/8年，無做手術。放棄咗踢波，個骨科醫生唔建議我做，另外搵過一個骨科專家都話必要性唔大。佢建議我操腳，佢仲同我講外國有網球員都係acl 無做手術都可以照打波。佢叫我做手術不如搵人操好腳。唔好無端端開一刀。<br />\n做咩運動都可以，不過有啲突然反應要出力嘅動作膝頭會痛。正常慢跑、游水、唔激烈打下藍球、羽毛球都可以。係驚年紀大咗之後啫。"},{"pid":"a04bc5d2beac6006a05dd71f08b08f14d88d1ead","tid":1132951,"uid":250415,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:48:40.000Z","msg":"其實斷咗唔一定要做手術 <br />\n<br />\n醫生話如果唔做劇烈運動就咁去操腳都ok 但係如果想做返啲有轉向 急停運動嘅話就建議做手術好啲<br />\n同埋唔做嘅話第時膝關節就會提早退化"},{"pid":"2da7375cf38489453ce7f2dbcdc1750fd64c2232","tid":1132951,"uid":106275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T08:14:26.000Z","msg":"做完手術差唔多兩個月 LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9258c85545e99f377b349a60ce312cbfd1bbeda","tid":1132951,"uid":73302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2da7375cf38489453ce7f2dbcdc1750fd64c2232","tid":1132951,"uid":106275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T08:14:26.000Z","msg":"做完手術差唔多兩個月 LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T11:15:49.000Z","msg":"家下點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f272837381b42c73f9f02e89d35f873babb083","tid":1132951,"uid":106275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9258c85545e99f377b349a60ce312cbfd1bbeda","tid":1132951,"uid":73302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2da7375cf38489453ce7f2dbcdc1750fd64c2232","tid":1132951,"uid":106275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T08:14:26.000Z","msg":"做完手術差唔多兩個月 LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T11:15:49.000Z","msg":"家下點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T13:08:35.000Z","msg":"可以行路，上到樓梯但落唔到樓梯 間中一下隻腳會無力<br />\n個膝頭仲有小小痛<br />\n小腿仲係麻脾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7972b55d613aed8c964de47eeb0e2b799d73c820","tid":1132951,"uid":79609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:01:24.000Z","msg":"術後四個月<br />\n努力操返四頭肌"},{"pid":"80395eedab45cee73f4692fa7fe95c68a3ee38a7","tid":1132951,"uid":33345,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:16:49.000Z","msg":"斷咗4個月都未做手術，乜運動都無做<br />\n物理治療做咗兩個月又無做<br />\n放棄狀態<br />\n而家隻膝頭有時扭到都feel到移位，仲要痛個隻<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e189d86050e726a480fbfe1609264709bdb03850","tid":1132951,"uid":14023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T07:12:48.000Z","msg":"左腳斷過兩次，第一次2008 年第二次2014年，批走埋半月板，斷完第一次做運動仲多咗但跳躍動作唔係太敢，再斷就係打羽毛球jumpsmash 落地。2015 年做完第二次手術而家仲會繼續做運動，游渡海泳，跑10k都可以（跑完腳有d痛），除咗唔跳同跪係到有野頂住，落雨風濕之外，一切如常。"}]}